think TRON — literally: every program in the grid is cast from a User in the world outside it.
the carbon character is the program; this file is its User. in TRON the actor plays BOTH.

the program (in-world) : Sam Flynn — the heir · the User who went in
the User (carbon)      : Garrett Hedlund  [ the actor — who plays the User and the Program ]
the analog (your world): the inheritor who must decide what to do with a creator-parent's legacy
